{"id": "1474839073087553696", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "跟朋友聊了一下列車劇情，突然意識到除了時間線問題還有一個守密人ooc的問題，於是 <@874937440605974549> 得出列車劇情全是N的推測<:Brown_think:1459080117308620996>", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:43:56.209000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:44:15.166000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["874937440605974549"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474840618852417791", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "有點同意，說實話守咪人有太多地方可以加點「怎麼才能逃出密境」「這是個夢的話我要怎麼醒過來」等等的想法/思考方面的描寫", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:50:04.748000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474840948642021643", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是沒有這麼做的原因是什麼？因為這是真實發生的事？因為守咪人不覺得自己被困在人工密境之類的東西裡？", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:51:23.376000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474841511480004670", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果這是真實事件，那這從時間線上就說不通，如果這只是密境、夢境、幻覺，那為什麼守密人沒有任何一點疑惑或警惕？", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:53:37.567000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474841595512619161", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "那个，我突然又有别的想法了(\n守密人不思考好像也是合理的了，毕竟他遇上N了，已经不是梦不梦，密境不密境的问题了XD", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:53:57.602000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:54:10.948000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474841641943830640", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "草", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:54:08.672000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474842175014699008", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "可是N也「只是」質體，做不到這種既不是密境也不是夢……嘶，我隱約記得夢好像是可以的，某個特遣好像有這樣的描寫，但是……🧐", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:56:15.766000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474842594528858322", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "只是时间线确实令人费解，这个守密人看着又像忘却篇时期(开头他说他只想回宿舍装尸体)，又像星辰篇时期(想回到弥萨格和拉蒙娜的身边)", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:57:55.786000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["614083839131648021"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1474841511480004670", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474843127830413565", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "我的大脑放弃思考了，这种冲突矛盾的点姑且当作这是N扮起我们守密人后的样子吧<:Salvador_OK:1468258324066734305> (？)", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:00:02.935000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474844233763524678", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為我偶爾能理解編劇想要什麼而有點先入為主的覺得這是星辰篇的守咪魂穿忘卻海國之前的時間，你說的回宿舍裝屍體確實乍看不太像星辰咪，但是忘卻咪也說過自己的夢想是當廢物，按照合理的人物邏輯也可以這樣理解：咪其實想要回到普通的日常生活。但是這樣解讀的話，會比較像是夢境裡潛意識的渴求(？)，就是做夢可以不合邏輯但偶爾也合乎情感邏輯🧐", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:04:26.610000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Brown_think", "emoji_id": "1459080117308620996", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474844909650313268", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "参考莱克的特遣纪录，这可能是梦，但还是有地方说不清，或者说只是因为我们的视角“小”，几乎只有守密人视角，而且没有关于“梦”的描述(比如说后来有没有醒来", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:07:07.754000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["614083839131648021"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1474842175014699008", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474845816647581726", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "隔壁和列車有關的遊戲不是有首和夢有關的歌的歌詞是什麼「別忘了閉上眼才算醒來」嗎？說不定後面真的醒了呢<:Brown_think:1459080117308620996>", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:10:43.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:11:05.068000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474847105842676024", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "我的理論一直偏向星辰咪魂穿忘卻海國之前那個時間段的，但是我的理論仍然有個未知數/漏洞，就是「借用分身的身體」這件事是不是可以「跨時空」的，因為整個理論建立在「可以」這個答案的前提上，但是如果「可以」，N的能力不就比我想像中還強大？可以借用任意時間段/世界線的自己的分身，這可以相當於可以預知未來了吧？🧐", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:15:51.367000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474847580675379281", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且就算真的是星辰咪魂穿，那「魂穿的咪到底是從星辰篇哪個時間段穿過來的」也是個問題<:Tulu_sleep2:1468259861598044402>", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:17:44.576000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474847974000693493", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "614083839131648021", "author_name": "shostakovich524", "author_bot": false, "content": "話說N的權柄到底是可以幹嘛的(", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:19:18.352000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1474847105842676024", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474848050470981722", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果其实「跨时空」只是N又生成了另外一场梦(或者说弄了另一个情景剧情)，让剧情看起来像跨时空呢(？)", "timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:19:36.584000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-21T19:21:12.570000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["614083839131648021"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1474847105842676024", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
